SYSTEM CALLS

Write C Program for:

File management related – create/delete file…

Information maintenance related- get/set time/date

SPOT EXERCISE

Write C programs for the following problems:

1. Copy the contents of an existing file to another file (check if the destination file already exists, if so get permission to overwrite it from the user, before copying).

2. What will be the date and time after 2 days from now (can assume any valid time or system time for now)?
